{"tid":845723,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone XS 三大問題","createTime":"2018-10-03T01:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T15:02:49.000Z","uid":209701,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"06248285e93f42fbaa57f41628fb7baef693fee5","tid":845723,"uid":209701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/093047_1f45de0837b9c29449fe83791a3ef4f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F093047_1f45de0837b9c29449fe83791a3ef4f6.jpg&h=d5b3f9be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\no岩o岩見到有位台灣網民列出新iPhone既三大問題<br />\n<br />\n如果係蘋果死忠fans既，可以略過<br />\n<br />\n想買XS既，不妨望下.....<br />\n<br />\n自從iPhone 4開始，偶爾都會傳出一些iPhone的門 &ldquo;Gate&rdquo; 事件。<br />\niPhone 4 的 AntennaGate<br />\niPhone 6 的 BendGate<br />\niPhone 6S 的 BatteryGate<br />\n<br />\n出現這些門事件的時候，蘋果有時會想一些補償措施（電池更換折扣），<br />\n有時會推卸責任：<br />\n&ldquo;你握iPhone的方式錯了&rdquo;、&ldquo;你的褲子太緊了&rdquo;<br />\n所以蘋果的門事件一直都是3C界的一大熱門話題<br />\n<br />\n來看看近期 iPhoneXS 推出後，出現了什麼 &rdquo;門事件&ldquo; 呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dcard.tw/f/3c/p/229769312?utm_source=gadge&amp;utm_medium=post&amp;utm_campaign=229769312&amp;utm_content=201810033C1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcard.tw%2Ff%2F3c%2Fp%2F229769312%3Futm_source%3Dgadge%26utm_medium%3Dpost%26utm_campaign%3D229769312%26utm_content%3D201810033C1&d=vafsAJtW1FASTd9W%2FbGZwqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=857a43ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcard.tw/f/3c/p/229769312?utm_source=gadge&amp;utm_medium=post&amp;utm_campaign=229769312&amp;utm_content=201810033C1</a>"},{"pid":"90ec9da0f173d687ecfc5ca24fe02c3d1bdeee5e","tid":845723,"uid":37688,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:37:15.000Z","msg":"屌你 係要人禁入條link黎睇 唔識po出黎？"},{"pid":"14106453f4a787ee0c30cbd37775150822fb4f21","tid":845723,"uid":133,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:34:57.000Z","msg":"來看看近期 iPhoneXS 推出後，出現了什麼 &rdquo;門事件&ldquo; 呢？<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n【充電門事件 ChargeGate】<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n這是個人覺得今年最嚴重的門事件。<br />\n<br />\n&rdquo;某些iPhone在未解鎖前插入Lightning時無法充電，<br />\n必須要把螢幕點甦醒了才會開始充電&ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n雖然聽起來不像大問題，但如果你是那種晚上睡覺前插一下就丟旁邊充電，隔天準備上班才發現根本沒充到，真的會是一個嚴重的困擾。<br />\n據電池專家表示，這是內建電池管理系統予Lightning插頭之間認證的問題，是可以用軟體來更正的。<br />\n希望蘋果盡快處理好這個問題，不然災情鬧大了真的會一發不可收拾。<br />\n<br />\n以下是UnboxTherapy對於ChargeGate的說明：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/J_lRJuQtBmc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJ_lRJuQtBmc&d=vafsAJtW1FASTd9W%2FbGZwqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=cbf2eb7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/J_lRJuQtBmc</a><br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n【美肌門 BeautyGate】<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n隨著iPhone XS推出的Super HDR，前鏡頭好像也出現了一個新的現象 - 自動美肌<br />\n開了前鏡頭的Super HDR 時，皮膚會變得光滑很多<br />\n關掉Super HDR時會稍微改善，但自動美肌依然還在<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.dcard.tw/kSAbPCh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.dcard.tw%2FkSAbPCh.jpg&h=3100b9c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.dcard.tw/Eu4EuE8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.dcard.tw%2FEu4EuE8.jpg&h=b8622ed1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然美肌對於多數東方客群而言都不是個問題<br />\n但這真的很不像一向來主打影像準確的蘋果會做的事情啊！<br />\n<br />\n目前多數網友的訴求是希望<br />\n可以有【關掉這種自動美肌的選擇】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n【BlueShift】<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n不確定這會不會成為一個話題，但看你個人是不是完美主義者吧<br />\n蘋果自iPhone XS 開始決定把OLED螢幕生產線分散，<br />\n一部分由三星代工，另一部分由LG代工<br />\n三星代工的OLED基本上跟去年iPhone X 沒什麼太大差別<br />\n但LG代工的OLED出現了所謂的BlueShift現象<br />\n也就是在特定的角度觀看螢幕時，純白色會開始稍微偏藍<br />\n<br />\n三星的OLED大概斜視45-60度以上才會開始出現色偏<br />\n但LG的OLED在大概30-45度就開始出現色偏了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.dcard.tw/lWxlsXe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.dcard.tw%2FlWxlsXe.jpg&h=5e782fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這現象在去年的Pixel 2引起了很大的一波騷動，<br />\n有些人為了這件事而退換了很多台手機<br />\niPhone XS 會不會也出現如此的現象呢？<br />\n你買的iPhone XS 螢幕中獎了嗎？三星或是LG？<br />\n<br />\nYoutuber對於 BlueShift 說明：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HOeFOgFgAEI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHOeFOgFgAEI&d=vafsAJtW1FASTd9W%2FbGZwqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6a5f78ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HOeFOgFgAEI</a>"},{"pid":"c365f75e6b122a05606064b326b245554521395f","tid":845723,"uid":133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:35:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">OP正懶西</span></span>"},{"pid":"5dc7ad41a24077ca209e26aeafc7f1b0e4bd0a64","tid":845723,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T05:15:56.000Z","msg":"發熱耗電問題咁嚴重無人講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4031e25af28e7cc63168bfb4354a1adf7ac656f","tid":845723,"uid":20890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:37:51.000Z","msg":"信號接收問題呢？"},{"pid":"f2f45cb2276ebaf789fd9949986a5308ebdb2e8c","tid":845723,"uid":105500,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.dcard.tw/kSAbPCh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.dcard.tw%2FkSAbPCh.jpg&h=3100b9c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n條女幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4516089ee6340904c96af470c78ee010dc961ff7","tid":845723,"uid":131625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4031e25af28e7cc63168bfb4354a1adf7ac656f","tid":845723,"uid":20890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime